# py-aiger-cnf
Python library to convert between AIGER and CNF

[![Build Status](https://cloud.drone.io/api/badges/mvcisback/py-aiger-cnf/status.svg)](https://cloud.drone.io/mvcisback/py-aiger-cnf)
